#: app/templates/tasklist.html:28
msgid ""
"We'll also ask you to upload a business plan to support the answers "
"you've given us in the management case section."
msgstr ""
"Byddwn hefyd yn gofyn i chi lanlwytho cynllun busnes i ategu'r atebion "
"rydych wedi'u rhoi i ni yn yr adran achos rheoli."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:32
msgid "Moving through the form"
msgstr "Symud drwy'r ffurflen"

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:35
msgid "This form is split into sections based on how it will be assessed."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r ffurflen hon wedi'i rhannu'n adrannau ar sail y modd y caiff ei "
"hasesu."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:38
msgid "You do not have to complete it in order, or all at once."
msgstr "Nid oes rhaid i chi ei llenwi mewn trefn, na'r cyfan ar unwaith."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:41
msgid ""
"When you have written something in every field in a section, the section "
"will be marked as complete. You can still change your responses in "
"sections that are marked as complete."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch wedi ysgrifennu rhywbeth ym mhob maes mewn adran, cofnodir yr"
" adran fel un gyflawn. Gallwch newid eich ymatebion o hyd mewn adrannau "
"sydd wedi'u cofnodi fel rhai cyflawn."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:45
msgid "Saving progress and making changes"
msgstr "Cadw cynnydd a gwneud newidiadau"

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:48
msgid ""
"Your work will not save automatically. To make sure you do not lose "
"anything, select Save and continue regularly, and always before you go "
"back or close your internet browser window."
msgstr ""
"Ni fydd eich gwaith yn cael ei gadw'n awtomatig. I wneud yn siŵr nad "
"ydych chi'n colli unrhyw beth, dewiswch 'Cadw' a pharhau'n rheolaidd, a "
"bob amser cyn i chi fynd yn ôl neu gau eich ffenestr porwr rhyngrwyd."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:51
msgid "If you need to edit or revisit any sections, use the browser back button."
msgstr ""
"Os oes angen i chi olygu neu fynd yn ôl at unrhyw adrannau, defnyddiwch "
"fotwm nôl y porwr."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:54
msgid "You can edit your responses as many times as you like before you submit."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch olygu'ch ymatebion gymaint o weithiau a fynnwch cyn i chi eu "
"cyflwyno."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:58
msgid "Submitting your application"
msgstr "Cyflwyno'ch cais"

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:61
msgid ""
"When you have completed all sections, you'll be able to submit your "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch wedi llenwi'r holl adrannau, byddwch yn gallu cyflwyno'ch "
"cais."

#: app/templates/tasklist.html:64
msgid ""
"Once you have submitted your application, you'll not be able to edit, add"
" or change any sections."
msgstr ""
"Wedi i chi gyflwyno'ch cais, ni fyddwch yn gallu golygu, ychwanegu na "
"newid unrhyw adrannau."

